title: The Training of O--------10692-Tara Lynn Foxx Day 2.
description:
From Kink.com     (The Training of O) + Pics





Four years spent working in the dungeon may seem like a long time from the outside looking in, but from the inside, it is here and gone in a flash. And besides, who would not wait four years for the day a girl like Miss Foxx offers herself up to whatever whims pop into one's twisted mind. Not that I would take advantage of the fine young lady or anything....but I do have a job to do. So, on your behalf, my perverted friends and enemies, let's take this bitch apart.
